      "     val_macroF1           val_balAcc           val_weightedF1          \n",
      "            mean       std       mean       std           mean       std\n",
      "seed                                                                    \n",
      "13      0.780516  0.249855   0.838696  0.247359       0.854082  0.232721\n",
      "21      0.763309  0.258821   0.832780  0.246118       0.847458  0.231377\n",
      "34      0.774682  0.253785   0.837835  0.246925       0.853114  0.232076\n",
      "\n",
      "[9B] Side-by-side means per seed:\n",
      "backbone       gcn       mlp\n",
      "seed                        \n",
