      "21        0.832780  0.783903\n",
      "34        0.837835  0.791638\n",
      "[9B] Saved all runs under: /home/rohit/Desktop/Projects/C-Elegans/track2_outputs/20250826_110441/runs_gcn/baselines_mlp_vs_gcn\n"
