      "[9C] all_blocks summary (mean±std across folds):\n",
      "     val_macroF1           val_balAcc           val_weightedF1          \n",
      "            mean       std       mean       std           mean       std\n",
      "seed                                                                    \n",
      "13      0.778869  0.250902   0.838481  0.247249       0.853838  0.232557\n",
      "21      0.742616  0.289122   0.819060  0.262577       0.831833  0.248663\n",
      "34      0.756864  0.269425   0.826576  0.259042       0.840371  0.245955\n",
